      "id": "61fe81ff_68c3fbb0",
      "file_path": "README.md",
      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 1,
      "message": "this README is related to the patch suggested by Thierry\nregarding the refactoring it is no more accurate.\n\nAs we are in the first step, the dev view and the tester view are maybe confusing.\nA good documentation for tester will be needed, which is different from the doc for developers.\nA README is enough to bootstrap\nwe need to have at least a way to test the structure through existing tests (even before merge)\n\nI like the idea to keep an example/sample dir\nas we need to replace the existing tests done in onap_tests, as samples we need to have\n- basic_vm\n- freeradius_nbi\n- clearwater_vims\n\nI suggest to add\n- vfw (as it is an illustration of the python SDK)\n- basic_network\n\nthe existing examples that were in the initial patch were\nrun_onboard.py => basic_vm_onboard\nrun_instantiate.py => basic_vm_instantiate\nrun_delete.py => delete resources\nrun_e2e.py => run_onboard.py + run_instantiate.py + run_delete.py",
